Bootstrap: localimage
From: ./ubuntu_22.04.sif

%post
    # Update package lists and install Python + pip
    apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends python3 python3-pip && \
    pip3 install --no-cache-dir pytest && \
    apt-get clean && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

    # Create the directory structure and the required input file
    mkdir -p /home/user/provisioning

    cat >/home/user/provisioning/hosts.txt <<'EOF'
web01
db01
web01
web02
db01
app01
web02
web02
db01
EOF

    # Ensure the student (non-root at runtime) can read/write inside /home/user
    chmod -R a+rwx /home/user

%labels
    chmod 755 /home/user

    Author      "Apptainer Task Prep"
    Description "Environment for hostname frequency summarization task with pytest available."

%help
This container provides the initial state for the hostname frequency
summarization task.  It contains:
  • /home/user/provisioning/hosts.txt – the raw host list.
  • pytest – installed system-wide for automated grading.
No output file has been pre-created; the student must generate
/home/user/provisioning/host_frequencies.log as specified.